<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SevenNine Works | Coming Soon</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">
    <style>
        :root {
            --blue: #0066ff;
            --blue-bright: #1593ff;
            --ink: #10141b;
            --steel: #3f4a5a;
            --panel: rgba(246, 248, 252, 0.94);
            --panel-border: rgba(70, 88, 112, 0.26);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 32px 18px;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.22), transparent 34%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 18% 80%, rgba(21, 147, 255, 0.14), transparent 30%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2f7 0%, #d8dee8 46%, #b9c3d1 100%);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.22) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.22) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 46px 46px;
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black, transparent 74%);
            opacity: 0.38;
        }

        .card {
            position: relative;
            width: min(100%, 680px);
            padding: 52px 42px 46px;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow:
                0 28px 80px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.24),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52) inset;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 14px;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,102,255,0.16), transparent 48%, rgba(0,102,255,0.09));
            filter: blur(22px);
        }

        .logo-wrap {
            margin: 0 auto 26px;
            padding: 18px 18px 10px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 44%, rgba(255,255,255,0.9), rgba(229,235,245,0.42) 62%, rgba(255,255,255,0));
        }

        .logo {
            display: block;
            width: min(100%, 500px);
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 18px 24px rgba(16, 20, 27, 0.26));
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.56);
            color: #0057dc;
            background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.08);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--ink);
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            line-height: 1.08;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            width: 118px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), var(--blue-bright), transparent);
            margin: 22px auto;
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--steel);
            line-height: 1.65;
            margin: 10px auto;
            max-width: 520px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            color: #263140;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: #687488;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 560px) {
            body {
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 22px;
            }

            .card {
                padding: 34px 20px 32px;
                border-radius: 22px;
            }

            .logo-wrap {
                padding: 10px 4px 4px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .badge {
                font-size: 10px;
                letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main class="card" aria-label="SevenNine Works coming soon">
        <div class="logo-wrap">
            <img src="logo_1920x1080.png" alt="SevenNine Works Logo" class="logo">
        </div>

        <div>
            <span class="badge">Custom 3D Printing</span>
        </div>

        <h1>SevenNine Works is coming soon.</h1>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="tagline">Practical parts, personalized designs, and small-batch 3D prints.</p>
        <p>Check back soon as we get everything dialed in.</p>

        <footer>Made with care. Printed with purpose.</footer>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
